It's been two weeks since this whole thing started.

He asks his wife if she has seen the car. "Yes dear, but that doesn't make you any less special." The next day, several cars are spotted in town with "#1 Dad" painted on the sides. The fathers are worried that they might not be the "#1 Dad" anymore. By the end of the week, cars were lining up at detail shops to get "#1 Dad" painted on their cars and trucks. Soon, even vehicles that aren't cars are sporting "#1 Dad" on them. Tractors, semis, helicopters. One person spotted an ambulance with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, not by the driver but by the passenger's wife! Early the next day, Air Force One was caught landing in front of the White House with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, and even printed on the jackets of the Secret Service. 
It's been two weeks since this whole thing started.
 Now, every vehicle in the country belongs to the #1 Dad. But no one knows who the best dad actually is. The country is very concerned about this. "The One has to be out there somewhere among us. We have to find him." 
Meanwhile, the #1 Dad is out for a walk.

The fathers are worried that they might not be the "#1 Dad" anymore. By the end of the week, cars were lining up at detail shops to get "#1 Dad" painted on their cars and trucks. Soon, even vehicles that aren't cars are sporting "#1 Dad" on them. Tractors, semis, helicopters. One person spotted an ambulance with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, not by the driver but by the passenger's wife! Early the next day, Air Force One was caught landing in front of the White House with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, and even printed on the jackets of the Secret Service. 
It's been two weeks since this whole thing started.
 Now, every vehicle in the country belongs to the #1 Dad. But no one knows who the best dad actually is. The country is very concerned about this. "The One has to be out there somewhere among us. We have to find him." 
Meanwhile, the #1 Dad is out for a walk.

The #1 Dad smiles and picks up the mug. "You are the best dad in the world." says the son. "I love you."

"Thanks, son." says the #1 Dad. "I love you too." And that is how an ordinary man bec

One person spotted an ambulance with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, not by the driver but by the passenger's wife! Early the next day, Air Force One was caught landing in front of the White House with "#1 Dad" painted on the side, and even printed on the jackets of the Secret Service. 
It's been two weeks since this whole thing started.
